            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1683034839748-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1683034839748-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>ground</strong> <strong>allspice</strong> in a large mixing bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span> each of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, then add the<strong> chicken breast portions </strong>and coat thoroughly</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated chicken breast portions</strong> and cook on each side for 3 min</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1683034855486-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
