    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, boil half a kettle</p><p>Chop the <strong>dried</strong> <strong>cranberries</strong> coarsely</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped cranberries</strong> to a bowl, then cover with <strong>boiled water</strong> and set aside to soften</p>",
