    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>blanched</strong> <strong>almonds</strong> to a separate tray, drizzle them with a little <strong>olive oil</strong> and place them in the oven for 5 min or until slightly darkened in colour</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p><p>Once done, remove from the oven and sprinkle with <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Leave them to cool on the tray</p>",
